Question:-

WAP to find out if 1st January will be a Sunday between 2000 and 2030


Answer:-

for(var year = 2000; year <= 2030; year++){
    var date = new Date(year, 0, 1);
    if(date.getDay() === 0){
        console.log(` 1st Jan is Sunday in ${year}`);
    }
}


Output:-

VM2945:4  1st Jan is Sunday in 2006
VM2945:4  1st Jan is Sunday in 2012
VM2945:4  1st Jan is Sunday in 2017
VM2945:4  1st Jan is Sunday in 2023
